{"tid":268816,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天氣專家食屎啦","createTime":"2017-06-03T10:03:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T11:04:02.000Z","uid":24335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6a97a1e0ecdedb185b12423ffe83247070a28ed","tid":268816,"uid":24335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:03:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170603&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=56778748 說好的大驟雨呢？天文台為「失準」解畫\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170603%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D56778748%20%E8%AA%AA%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E9%A9%9F%E9%9B%A8%E5%91%A2%EF%BC%9F%E5%A4%A9%E6%96%87%E5%8F%B0%E7%82%BA%E3%80%8C%E5%A4%B1%E6%BA%96%E3%80%8D%E8%A7%A3%E7%95%AB&d=soNRc1toP2VYVWC%2FYI%2BOFPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=6726e753\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170603%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D56778748%20%E8%AA%AA%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E9%A9%9F%E9%9B%A8%E5%91%A2%EF%BC%9F%E5%A4%A9%E6%96%87%E5%8F%B0%E7%82%BA%E3%80%8C%E5%A4%B1%E6%BA%96%E3%80%8D%E8%A7%A3%E7%95%AB&h=402b1eb5\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170603&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=56778748 說好的大驟雨呢？天文台為「失準」解畫</a><br />\n<br />\n天文台日前預計，一道低壓槽在周末期間襲港，今日雨勢最大，有「大驟雨」，雖其後調弱雨勢預測，惟最終今日竟天睛酷熱。天文台解釋，因該低壓槽主要在本港以北徘徊，而大雨亦集中在廣州和本港東北面附近，故香港天氣比預期好，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但強調跟預測並非相差太遠。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n天文台高級科學主任李新偉回覆《蘋果》查詢時指，與該低壓槽相關的大雨，今日集中在本港北至東北面，加上這些因對流發展的雨區，範圍小，亦較為隨機和短促，「唔一定落正某啲地方」，最終香港沒有大驟雨，天氣較預期好。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁都叫唔係相差太遠, 天文台成班都讀屎片垃圾</span></span>"},{"pid":"3ff847c7263933f67b54eacc0a22fc2dcf308178","tid":268816,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/03/180439_540af21bdf6d00aab855d7187d18ef27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"